{"tid":96083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"晚上, 是男人了解自己寂寞的時候","createTime":"2017-01-26T14:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T09:33:38.000Z","uid":61920,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65712e42eaeef1d0cd01b7a06899c073c8b3f3f4","tid":96083,"uid":61920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:03:19.000Z","msg":"工作了整天<br />\n朝九晚五, 舟車勞頓<br />\n雖則白天工作沒甚麼壓力<br />\n因為永遠的冗員是永遠的快樂<br />\n工作時工作, 放工時放工<br />\n下班後<br />\n有時跟豬朋們飯局<br />\n有時球類運動一下, 再飯局<br />\n有時玩玩自己的興趣<br />\n有時歸家充一充乖仔吃住家飯<br />\n嗯...<br />\n感覺多姿多彩聲色畫盡現<br />\n酒肉穿腸過<br />\n開心有幾多<br />\n其實每一個晚上<br />\n最想的<br />\n都是自己一個單獨的靜一靜<br />\n在屬於自己的地方<br />\n發著呆<br />\n冥想著<br />\n呼出悶苦煙<br />\n喝下刺烈酒<br />\n躺著<br />\n頹著<br />\n眼睜開又不知望何處<br />\n心在跳但尤如停了頓<br />\n想想年少輕狂的快樂<br />\n想想來年擔憂的人生<br />\n矛盾只因思覺象<br />\n試問世間上知道自己的人有幾多<br />\n歡笑掛在臉<br />\n憂傷藏心裡<br />\n太陽底下永遠都是堅強的麻甩佬<br />\n月亮照著頓時顯現小子的玻璃心<br />\n酒過三巡 話多了<br />\n其實直正的男人 大多都寡言<br />\n今日就講到呢度<br />\n繼續飲先<br />\nbye"},{"pid":"435ae48b5ae233d4765a0f8b1432ccf329516d39","tid":96083,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082fcf129e1d834bfae436dff37546084e411a56","tid":96083,"uid":16770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2c785a8a5afc71499696bc5c80b38f13dabbde","tid":96083,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffeff095931a8368e1b669b45d4f07b5bc691dd8","tid":96083,"uid":61920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"明天繼續返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e781f1eb831668a095d7d78bbe22583aefbec5","tid":96083,"uid":17896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:37:13.000Z","msg":"巴打, 你好似無女咁喎"},{"pid":"d97077def4d72f364ad84b4b26e7ef7d19c8f5b5","tid":96083,"uid":37516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:38:39.000Z","msg":"朝九晚五<br />\n巴打真好"},{"pid":"4b3a222c628f8c120c3b2e27c80408ed70e76cae","tid":96083,"uid":20730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"唔知點解睇到眼濕濕灰撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ee24b90e7b7341e41af20f475c18cdd284157c","tid":96083,"uid":61920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:20:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打, 你好似無女咁喎</blockquote><br />\n女伴好多<br />\n但一個都唔想搵<br />\n因為傷過太多女人心"},{"pid":"19c0ec0d820989fe3c5c7621885f767d5bdbc857","tid":96083,"uid":61920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知點解睇到眼濕濕灰撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無咁誇呀巴打"},{"pid":"c1ad7752b53d930eaefacdf85962d196fb93fb63","tid":96083,"uid":7969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:23:49.000Z","msg":"有女又如何<br />\n只有自己明自己"},{"pid":"cb6c9d7befbffdfc734aa48bc7dd19d7ace7c1d5","tid":96083,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a5131855f863796de39138437222211eaee540","tid":96083,"uid":61920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:33:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有女又如何<br />\n只有自己明自己</blockquote><br />\n呢個的確<br />\n因為世上好難搵到一個真係明白自己<br />\n又或者可能係有時候<br />\n連自己想點都唔知<br />\n女人更甚<br />\n相信女人會想你比明佢更加多"}]}